title: Help please

replies.body: If you're building on a server, you need some sort of void world generator. On single player, you can search for a void world download on Google.
replies.body_tagged: If you're building on a server, you need some sort of void world generator. On single player, you can search for a void world download on Google.

replies.body: if you want a void map there is no seed you either download one off internet or make one by using presents if you want to use prestents in the box have this 0:1 for just void
replies.body_tagged: if you want a void map there is no seed you either download one off internet or make one by using presents if you want to use prestents in the box have this 0:1 for just void

replies.body: When I didn't have a server I used skyblock to start it off.
replies.body_tagged: When I didn't have a server I used skyblock to start it off.

replies.body: No there actually is a void seed. Select superflat and click custom. There's a bar and if you type 0,0 it should make a void world
replies.body_tagged: No there actually is a void seed. Select superflat and click custom. There's a bar and if you type 0,0 it should make a void world

replies.body: In general I create a void world with the preset 2;0 and I type /setblock ~ ~ ~ 42 So there is my first block and I continue the map.....
